  "*** ？？？：这样吗？那我不介意用仪式残留的力量来消灭你们这些蝼蚁 ***": {
    "translation": "",
    "MultiLang": {
      "US": "*** ??? : Is that so? Then I have no objection to using the power left over from the ritual to eliminate you ants. ***",
